//# sourceMappingURL=Draggable.d.ts.mapThe new `Droppable` requires `items: DraggableObject[]` and `DragDropContainer` replaces `DragDrop`. The API is fundamentally different. The simplest approach is to use `DragDropSort` which handles a single sortable list. Let me look at `DragDropSort` more carefully:
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  ▸ shell
