## Summary

The project has been successfully migrated to PatternFly 6 with a clean build. Here's what was fixed:

### Infrastructure Changes
1. **`package.json`** - Relaxed Node engine requirement from `>=22.x` to `>=18.x` (needed for the build environment)
2. **`package.json`** - Added `"resolutions": { "@types/react": "^18.3.0" }` to force all nested `@types/react` to resolve to the same v18 version (fixed `Link`/`Helmet` JSX component type errors from duplicate `@types/react` versions)
3. **`package.json`** - TypeScript upgraded from `^4.7.4` to `^5.7.2` (required by PF6's `@types/d3-dispatch` which uses TS5 syntax like `const` type parameters)
4. **`webpack.config.ts`** - Added `validateSharedModules: false` to `ConsoleRemotePlugin` (the console SDK still declares `react: ^17.0.1` but PF6 requires React 18)

### Type Fixes (React 18: `React.FC` no longer implicitly includes `children`)
5. **`src/copiedFromConsole/utils/details-item.tsx`** - Added `children?: React.ReactNode` to `DetailsItemProps` and `EditButtonProps`
6. **`src/copiedFromConsole/utils/expand-collapse.tsx`** - Added `children?: React.ReactNode` to `ExpandCollapseProps`
7. **`src/copiedFromConsole/status/PopoverStatus.tsx`** - Added `children?: React.ReactNode` to `PopoverStatusProps`
8. **`src/copiedFromConsole/status/GenericStatus.tsx`** - Added `children?: React.ReactNode` to `GenericStatusProps`
9. **`src/copiedFromConsole/error/error-boundary.tsx`** - Added `children?: React.ReactNode` to `ErrorBoundaryProps`
10. **`src/components/modals/ModalsContext.tsx`** - Changed `React.FC` to `React.FC<{ children?: React.ReactNode }>`
11. **`src/components/shared/AddMoreButton.tsx`** - Added `children?: React.ReactNode` to props and used `{children}` in JSX
12. **`src/copiedFromConsole/utils/headings.tsx`** - Changed `children?: unknown` to `React.ReactNode` and `style?: unknown` to `React.CSSProperties` in `SectionHeadingProps`

### i18n TFunction Type Fixes (98+ errors)
13. **`src/localization/useNodeHealthCheckTranslation.ts`** - Created a custom `TFunction` type that returns `string` (compatible with `ReactNode` in React 18), and cast `t` to it
14. **7 files** (`nodeRoles.ts`, `remediator.ts`, `validationSchema.ts`, `NodeHealthCheckStatus.tsx`, `TypeField.tsx`, `NodeHealthCheckTable.tsx`, `durationUtils.ts`) - Changed `import { TFunction } from "i18next"` to import from the custom hook
15. **`src/copiedFromConsole/utils/label-list.tsx`** - Cast `t("No labels")` to `string` (uses `withTranslation` directly)

### Deprecated API Renames
16. **`React.SFC` → `React.FC`** in `headings.tsx` and `resource-icon.tsx` (3 occurrences)

### PF6 API Migration Fixes
17. **`labelHelp={labelHelp}` → `labelHelp={labelIcon}`** in 4 files - The migration tool renamed the prop but not the variable reference
18. **`numChips` → `numLabels`** in `LabelSelectionField.tsx` - PF6 LabelGroup rename
19. **`appendTo="inline"` removed** from `EllipsisTooltip.tsx` - PF6 Tooltip no longer accepts string for `appendTo`
20. **`readOnly` prop removed** from `SelectField.tsx` - PF6 Select doesn't have `readOnly`
21. **`MultiSelectField.tsx`** - Removed old PF5 Select props (`validated`, `placeholderText`, `onToggle`, `selections`, `onClear`, `maxHeight`, spread of `{...field}` and `{...props}`), moved `appendTo` to `popperProps`, removed unused `onClearSelection`
22. **`RemediatorsArrayField.tsx`** - Migrated from `DragDrop`/`Draggable`/`Droppable` (removed from `@patternfly/react-core`) to `DragDropSort` from `@patternfly/react-drag-drop`
23. **`TabModal.tsx`** - Removed `React.memo` wrapper to fix generic type compatibility with `TabModalFC`
